quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,25,"Min Nulaani ado maa…óa immorde e Nulaa…óo si wonaa Min mbahayinii e makko; pellet, dewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Min ndewee Kam."
  21,26,"∆Āe mbi'i wi'i: "jurmotoo…óo O jogitike …ďi…ó…óo". Senaare woodanii mo, ko woni, […ďen ko …ďe] jiyaa…ďe teddinaa…ďe."
  21,27,"∆Āe adortaa mo konngol ngol, kam…ďe ko Yamiroore makko nden …ďe ngollata."
  21,28,"Homo Anndi ko woni ko yeeso ma…ď…ďe e ko woni ko …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, …ďe tefanoytaa si wanaa on mo o Weltanii, kam…ďe immorde e kulol makko ko …ďe jootu…ďe."
  21,29,"Kala e ma…ď…ďe kadi bi'i…óo: "min ko mi dewetee…óo gaanin makko". On …óo Min njo…ďat mo Jahanna- ma ko wano nii Min njo…ďirta too√Īoo…ďe …ďen."
  21,30,"Enee, …ďen yeddu…ďe yiaani won'dema kammuuji …ói e leydi ndi …ói laatinoke kippondir…ói, Min ngudditi …ói Min mba…ói immorde e ndiyam …óam kala hu'unde wuuru nde. Kaa …ďe ngon…óintaa?"
  21,31,"Min mba…ói a…ói ka leydi pelle fii wata nde oo√Īodo e ma…ď…ďe, Min mba…ói a…ói e mayri …óate jaacu…óe, mbelejo'o kam…ďe …ďe peewat."
  21,32,"Min mba…ói kammu ngun kippu…ói reenaandi, kam…ďe ko …ďe …óurnii…ďe ga aayeeje amen …óe."
  21,33,"Ko KaŇčko woni On Tak…óo jemma on e √Īalawma on e na'ange nge e lewru ndun kala majji hi…ói fubboo(lummboo) ka fuluku."
  21,34,"Min mba…óanaani …ďanndunke ado maa…óa luttineede, enee, si a maayii ko kam…ďe ngoni luttintee…ďe …ďen?"
  21,35,"Kala woŇčkii meedat maay…óe nde, Min njarribora on bone on e mo∆ī∆īere nde njarrabagol, ko ka amen kadi nduttoto…óon."